OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FCouncils told to consider  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fresidents' support of LTNs 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Councils in England will have to       
OL,6, consider local residents' views before 
OL,7, introducing new low traffic            
OL,8, neighbourhoods (LTNs) under new        
OL,9, government guidance.                   
OL,11,FIn LTNs, vehicles are stopped from     
OL,12,Fusing some residential roads.          
OL,14,FThe draft guidance says councils should
OL,15,Fbe confident such a scheme has the     
OL,16,Fsupport of most of the community.      
OL,18,FLabour accused ministers of trying to  
OL,19,F"dictate to local communities how they 
OL,20,Fuse their streets".                    
